sent.orig: Papain as module enzyme was microencapsulated with ethocel in supercritical carbon dioxide gas anti-solvent (GAS) process.
sent.trans: 研究了以木瓜蛋白酶为芯材，乙基纤维素为膜材的超临界流体抗溶剂(GAS)法制备酶微胶囊过程。

sent.orig: GAS is an open-source assembler on Linux.
sent.trans: GAS 是 Linux 环境下开放源码的汇编器。

sent.orig: GAS will produce the desired response in finite time receiving the client request.
sent.trans: GAS对于用户任一请求操作发生后的有限时间内总有对应的响应发生。

sent.orig: Special thanks to RAY, GAS, LHY and the teams help.
sent.trans: 另外特别鸣谢RAY,GAS,LHY和他们的团队鼎力支持帮忙。
